title: SWF Toolbox 3.5.19.275
description: SWF Toolbox enables you to convert Macromedia Flash Files (SWF) into standalone projector files (EXE), AVI movies, animated GIFs or frame-by-frame JPEG/GIF/BMP image series. The Advanced Projector option allows you to fully customize the projector with custom title, splash screen, optional expiration date, icon, file version, right-click options and other details, and can automatically install Flash OCX if not present on the system.
